<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[HELP!? (spoiler) I am confused about whether she accidentally kills R because of her poor driving skills and the dark (what she TOLD her mother) or if she wanted the R - her problem now - to disappear and purposely put her foot to the pedal (refer to one of the 3 things she will never tell her mother). Was it an accident or is the family covering for a cold blooded murder so they can get her to the Olympics? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
