</a><br/><br/>Devon is a star. That&apos;s all that matters.<br/><br/><a href='http://www.freeimagehosting.net/commercial-photography/' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1475427877ra/20720748.gif' alt='commercial photography locations' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a><br/><br/>Then for Devon herself. This young girl is a frigging robot. She is about to turn sixteen and knows that the worst thing ever is about to happen. She is about to get some boobs and curves. This is her las</span>
  <span id="freeText10899404291490017412" style="display:none">Katie and Eric Knox know no bounds when it comes to their extra-special gymnast daughter, Devon. Every thing goes to Devon and her amazing talent. That extra mortgage? No biggie. Smoozing with the richie bitch down the street. Par for the course. <br><a href="http://www.freeimagehosting.net/commercial-photography/" rel="nofollow noopener">
